genresAdvancedInfo.name: zenonesque
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A subgenre of psytrance that combines the psychedelic sounds of Goa trance with the calming and meditative qualities of Zen music. Zenonesque music is characterized by its slow and hypnotic beats, intricate melodies, and atmospheric soundscapes.
